{"tid":2429224,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"鯨大連英聯邦大學協會會員資格都無埋","createTime":"2021-03-02T06:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T10:48:32.000Z","uid":290404,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7745c2ba1c8d8d5512f3a7c46c8cba92c02e6bd7","tid":2429224,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:57:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的，英聯邦大學協會會員名冊入面本來有港大中大同埋鯨大，但最近會員名冊無左鯨大個名，剩得港大同中大<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.acu.ac.uk/our-members/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.acu.ac.uk%2Four-members%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=ab8af49a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.acu.ac.uk/our-members/</a><br />\n<br />\n之前問過鯨大果邊，校方確認左鯨大而家已經唔再係英聯邦大學協會成員，但唔肯講除名原因。<br />\n<br />\n台灣政府已經唔承認鯨大學歷，如今連英聯邦大學協會既資格都無左，讀鯨大既朋友想進修既話，可能要考慮留係大灣區。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9780fe0e8a9f4215ba51f423b0c14efb47e19e","tid":2429224,"uid":150100,"like":10,"dislike":58,"score":-48,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"其實OU易入難出，學生質素分分鐘好過八大好多"},{"pid":"ed9f532e98f4393fe751de24f6dfa3513873d44c","tid":2429224,"uid":290404,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3057b0a14c6b94e7ae9eb4b4ccbc46fcaef397","tid":2429224,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2f0961e5649703f76332f86bfe11d8039079b540","tid":2429224,"uid":110892,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"quote":{"pid":"6c9780fe0e8a9f4215ba51f423b0c14efb47e19e","tid":2429224,"uid":150100,"like":10,"dislike":58,"score":-48,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"其實OU易入難出，學生質素分分鐘好過八大好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:06:06.000Z","msg":"又係呢D ON9理論<br />\n易入係咩人都收<br />\n所以能力唔達標既人自然多<br />\n結果咪畢業囉"},{"pid":"ed43ed2dfa79498a8a5094e11f465961610a2fec","tid":2429224,"uid":284